;
; Animates the room indicator cursor (B channel). Identical logic to
; #R34967 (AnimateCrewA) but uses a faster frame rate (counter resets to 5
; rather than 10), the B-set animation table at #R26861 (#R26861), and the
; B-channel screen address at #R33736. Cycles through four cursor shapes
; (RoomCursor0-3) at twice the speed of the crew walk animation.
