; UpdateAlienEventTimer
;
; Decrements the secondary alien-event counter at #R33707 once per frame.
; When it reaches zero, the timer is reset to 255 and the routine moves on
; to fetch the next alien-event nibble from the ROM script and update the
; alien event state (corridor, target, action). If the primary alien-event
; timer at #R33706 is 255 (disabled), the routine returns immediately.
;
; Used by the routines at #R35578 and #R36457.
@nowarn=33706
