; BlitAlienFrame
;
; Advances AlienXPhase (0->1->2->3->0), loads the corresponding sprite frame pointer
; from the table at AlienXPhase+2, then LDIRs 6 bytes x 63 rows of sprite data to
; the display file at col 7, char-row 1, pixel-row 0, handling ZX Spectrum
; interleaved scan-line addressing at each row boundary.
