; DrawStatusPanel
@ignoreua
;
; Refreshes the crew-status display at the right side of the game window.
; Scans all 7 crew records starting at the alive-flag byte (#R29581 = $7386+7).
; For each crew member: if its crew-ID matches the alien's current target
; (#R33703) it is highlighted; if its alive flag is 0 (dead) the scan stops
; early (crew records are kept in alive-descending order). Live crew members
; get their portrait sprite drawn at the status panel position ($40A4 column).
;
; Used by the routine at #R36457.
@label=DrawStatusPanel
