; Zero-padding between game code and extra-data area
;
; 14146 bytes of zeros bridging the last byte of game code and the start
; of AlienFrame0 (#R60000). Reserved space in the runtime image; no code
; or data lives here. Note: a 16-bit constant inside this gap is used
; elsewhere as a Z80 I/O port number for the keyboard half-row
; B/N/M/SymShift/Space, not as a memory reference.
s45854 DEFS 14146
@ignoreua

